name: King Laugh Emote (Clash Royale)
description:
Clash Royale is a free, real time strategy mobile game developed and published by Supercell. The game is a spinoff of supercell's earlier mobile game Clash of Clans and features characters from said game. The game combines elements of card collecting, multiplayer battles, & tower defense.

The text "LVL 15" & "P2W" were added after recent controversy surrounding the game being pay-to-win.
